<html>
<head>
<title>Quick Bus Time</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
$(document).ready(function() {
    function goStop() {
        window.location = "s/" + $("#stopId").val();
    }

    $("#stopButton").click(goStop);
    $("#stopId").keypress(function(e) {
        if (e.which === 13) {
           goStop(); 
        }
    });

    function goRoute() {
        window.location = "r/" + $("#route").val().replace(" ", "/");
    }

    $("#routeButton").click(goRoute);

    $("#route").keypress(function(e) {
        if (e.which === 13) {
           goRoute(); 
        }
    });

});
</script>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Quick Bus Time</h1>

Stop Id.<br/>
On the bus stop sign.  If it says Text "CTABUS XXXX", XXXX is the stop id.<br/>
<input id="stopId" type="text" name="stopid" on/><br/>
<button id="stopButton">Go</button><br/><br/> 


Route<br/>
Ex. '151' or '151 N'<br/>
<input id="route" type="text" name="route" on/><br/>
<button id="routeButton">Go</button> 
</body>
</html>
